    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "It’s hot here. Everything is glowing.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Welcome to the Forge. Here, time is shaped through effort.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "What kind of effort?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "The kind that continues... and continues...",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Like something I’ll still be doing in the future?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Exactly. That’s Future Perfect Continuous.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "How does it work?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "We use ‘will have been’ and a verb with -ing.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "So, ‘I will have been working’?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Yes. And we add how long: ‘for five years’, ‘since Monday’.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "This sounds powerful.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Because it shows the effort before the result.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Let’s try using it.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
